title: Microsoft Azure: Agent Info
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the general state of the azure special agent.
 It reports the remaining API calls (which are limited by Microsoft),
 the monitored groups and encountered issues.

discovery:
 One service is created for each monitored resource group and one for the
 host that the agent is assigned to.
